data.description: Welcome to Wahoo Circle nestled on a quiet street right in the heart of the beautiful Bay Point Community! This spacious home features 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with a backyard oasis ready to be enjoyed year around with your family and friends. As you approach the home you are greeted by stunning Honduran Mahogany doors. Upon entry the vaulted ceilings and bright living area really showcase a coastal vibe as you overlook the pool and large backyard. Out back you will also find a fire pit for hosting many social gatherings or cozy nights with your family and plenty of space remains for storage and a swing set. This home has been updated throughout leaving no need for improvements. The large master bedroom features a spacious walk in closet and sliding glass doors for a late night dip in the pool. New roof, windows, and sliding glass doors, new water heater, and brand new pool liner. Too many more details to list, don't miss out on this opportunity of calling Bay Point in Panama City Beach HOME!** Seller is offering gas golfcart, some furnishings, garage refrigerator, and black tool chest with tools accompanying a full price offer.
